<html>
	<body style="font-family:Arial;font-size: 12pt;max-width: 575px;margin: auto;">
		<b>Hi  {!Receiving_User.FirstName},</b>
		<br/><br/>
		You recently requested to reset your password for your Insolvency Stream account.  Click the button below to reset it:
		<br/><br/>
		<div style="text-align:center;">
		<a href="{!Community_Url}" style="cursor:pointer;">
		<img src="https://c.na55.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015f1000003BklS&oid=00Dj0000001ripe&lastMod=1516614817000">
		</a>
		</div>
		<br/><br/>
		If you did not request a password reset, please disregard this email or reply to let us know.  This password reset link is only valid for the next 24 hours.
		<br/><br/><br/>
		<span style="font-style:italic;font-size: 10pt;">If you are having trouble clicking the password reset button above, copy and paste this URL into your web browser:<span>
		<br/><br/>
		<a href="{!Community_Url} " style="color: #092E6E;text-decoration: none;" >{!Community_Url} </a>
	</body>
</html>